These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, begonia, rose
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, pakistani, indian, italian
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, lemon, grapefruit, apricot
 1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the fan of rock is between the person who growspoppy and the person eating apricot##2
 3. the dutch is the person eating apricot##1
 4. the pakistani is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the person eating pineapple is between the person who growspoppy and the fan of reggae##2
 6. the italian is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the person eating lemon is the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Flower           | begonia | poppy   | rose | sunflower |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | disaster | drama              | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | funk     | rock               | reggae    |
| Nationality           | pakistani        | indian     | italian           | dutch       |
| Food     | lemon | grapefruit     | pineapple                | apricot      |

