.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina, bluemaster, bolivar
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, taxi, train
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, punk, r&b, techno
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, ivory, emerald, orange
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the van is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person who likes ivory##2
 4. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is the person driving the van##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the bluemaster-smoker##1
12. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Cigar          | bluemaster       | vegafina      | alhambra      | bolivar      |
| Transport           | train | van | taxi | bus |
| Music-Genre   | techno          | punk       | r&b            | gospel      |
| Color           | azure            | emerald    | ivory           | orange       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

