.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, banana, grapefruit, strawberry
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, mah-jongg, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, action, adventure, superhero
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, chess, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is between the person playing domino and the person who's sport is golf##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
11. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | asparagus  | strawberry | grapefruit |
| Game   | billiard   | mah-jongg        | domino | canasta     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | mystery    | superhero  | adventure   |
| Hobby           | chess     | woodworking      | hiking | skydiving        |
| Sport         | golf      | water-polo | rugby      | skiing     |

