.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, russian, dutch
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, epic, family, animation
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, roller, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the argentine##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching epic movies##2
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the engineer##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the engineer##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is between the engineer and the person driving the bus##2
 6. the pilot is on the far left##1
 7. the librarian is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person driving the van##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching family movies##2
10. the dutch is on the far left##1
11. the nigerian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage      | tea     | almond-milk | lemonade    | 7up          |
| Nationality          | dutch | argentine     | russian | nigerian         |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | epic       | animation         | thriller        |
| Job         | pilot  | librarian     | engineer     | paramedic |
| Transport     | bus     | roller      | quad-bike   | van          |

