.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, july, june
House: palace, art-deco, farmhouse, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, lemonade, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, lacrosse, tennis, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the french is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 6. the turkish is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the american is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 9. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
10. the townhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in february and the farmhouse house##2
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | february       | july       | june | january    |
| House         | art-deco     | townhouse | farmhouse | palace     |
| Beverage           | sprite        | milk    | lemonade  | coffee |
| Nationality   | american      | french      | turkish     | dutch     |
| Sport         | weightlifting | tennis      | lacrosse    | badminton |

