 6. the person who likes mauve is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who growsrose is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person traveling to marigolding##1
11. the person traveling to marigolding is between the social-worker and the person who growsrose##2
12. the person traveling to paris is between the person who growsazalea and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | coffee         | lemonade | juice      |
| Job           | social-worker | police-officer | designer | doctor     |
| Color   | turquise         | mauve          | ebony  | white |
| City         | rome        | marigolding  | paris | hannover   |
| Flower     | marigold    | lily         | rose     | azalea     |

