.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, tower, craftsman
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, analyst, librarian, coach
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, goldfish, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, swimming, tennis
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, iced-tea, fanta
 1. the owner of the snake is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the coach##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is the coach##1
 8. the analyst is on the right of the librarian##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the left of the librarian##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the craftsman house is between the coach and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

