.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, traveling, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, gospel, salsa
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, orchid, tulip
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, strawberry, apricot, broccoli
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, musical, adventure, documentary
 1. the fan of salsa is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who growstulip and the person eating grapefruit##2
 3. the person watching musical movies is between the person eating strawberry and the person watching adventure movies##2
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of gospel is the person eating apricot##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person who growszinnia is the person eating broccoli##1

